cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an invalid format will cause NG interface connection failures and prevent NGAP message exchange with the core network.

du.explanation_en: Setting downlink subcarrier spacing to invalid value 5 will cause serving cell configuration errors and prevent proper BWP setup for downlink transmissions.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行鏈路子載波間距設定為無效值 5 會導致服務小區配置錯誤，並阻止下行鏈路傳輸的正確 BWP 設定。
